data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This gorgeous single-story residence offers the perfect blend of style, space, and convenience. With four spacious bedrooms and three full bathrooms, this home is designed for comfort and versatility, ideal for families and those who appreciate the luxury of space. Step into the heart of this home, a gourmet kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and beautifully upgraded countertops. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or just love hosting gatherings, this kitchen is a masterpiece of modern design. Rich dark wood flooring flows throughout the home, enhancing its visual appeal and easy maintenance. The spacious family room, seamlessly connected to the kitchen, is the perfect place to entertain. The fully landscaped front and back yards are a gardener's delight. Step outside to your own private oasis. The charming front porch beckons you to sit and savor the neighborhood's tranquility.  This home is close to shopping and schools great location.
